<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Grope" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Grope,</orth> to feel along where one cannot see: <cit><quote>--ing for trouts in a peculiar river,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mm 1.2.91" default="NO" valid="yes">Meas. I, 2, 91</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>in the dark --d I to find out them,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 14</bibl></cit>.
